pim_schema:

PIM configuration

vrfs: object

VRF table

vrf: object[]

VRF name

object
vrf-name: string

VRF name

ipv4: AUTO-RP-DISABLE

IPV4 commands

ipv6: INTERFACE-TABLE

IPV6 commands

default-context: object

Default Context

ipv4:

IPV4 commands

ipv6:

IPV6 commands

Example
{
  "vrfs": {
    "vrf": [
      {
        "vrf-name": "string",
        "ipv4": {
          "auto-rp-disable": [ null ]
        },
        "ipv6": {
          "interfaces": {
            "interface": [
              {
                "enable": [ null ],
                "interface-name": "string",
                "override-interval": "integer"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "default-context": {
    "ipv4": {
      "interfaces": {
        "interface": [
          {
            "redirect-bundle": {
              "interface-bandwidth": "integer",
              "threshold-bandwidth": "integer",
              "bundle-name": "string"
            },
            "enable": [ null ],
            "interface-name": "string",
            "override-interval": "integer"
          }
        ]
      },
      "auto-rp-mapping-agent": {
        "parameters": {
          "interface-name": "string",
          "announce-period": "string",
          "ttl": "string"
        },
        "cache-limit": {
          "maximum-cache-entry": "integer",
          "threshold-cache-entry": "integer"
        }
      },
      "rpf-redirect": {
        "route-policy": "string"
      },
      "auto-rp-candidate-rps": {
        "auto-rp-candidate-rp": [
          {
            "protocol-mode": "string",
            "ttl": "string",
            "access-list-name": "string",
            "announce-period": "string",
            "interface-name": "string"
          }
        ]
      },
      "auto-rp-disable": [ null ]
    },
    "ipv6": {
      "interfaces": {
        "interface": [
          {
            "enable": [ null ],
            "interface-name": "string",
            "override-interval": "integer"
          }
        ]
      },
      "convergence": {
        "rpf-conflict-join-delay": "integer",
        "link-down-prune-delay": "integer"
      }
    }
  }
}

}

parameters_schema:

Specifications for Mapping Agent configured on this box

interface-name: string

Interface from which mapping packets will be sourced

announce-period: string

Time between discovery messages

ttl: string

TTL in Hops

Example
{
  "interface-name": "string",
  "announce-period": "string",
  "ttl": "string"
}

cache-limit_schema:

Mapping Agent cache size limit

maximum-cache-entry: integer

Maximum number of mapping cache entries

range:"1..1000"
threshold-cache-entry: integer

Warning threshold number of cache entries

range:"1..1000" default:"450"
Example
{
  "maximum-cache-entry": "integer",
  "threshold-cache-entry": "integer"
}
